        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/7005053.stm">BBC NEWS | TV cat poll was fixed, BBC says</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>I can forgive TV companies for running crooked competitions, or faking phone-ins, but overrulling the viewers&#8217; choice for the name for the Blue Peter Cat? That&#8217;s just EVIL!</p>

